<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ENTERTAINMENT-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Entertainment and culture stories in sight at this hour from The
N.Y. Times News Service for Wednesday, Oct. 14.
</P>
<P>
   BOSTON-BAD-ART (Boston) _ Arts in America: Boston's Museum of
Bad Art. By Carey Goldberg.
</P>
<P>
   CHRISTI-THEATER-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Corpus Christi,'' a
controversial play, at the Manhattan Theater Club. Reviewed by Ben
Brantley.
</P>
<P>
   Sidebars as needed.
</P>
<P>
   BEFORE-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Like Never Before,'' by Ehud
Havagelet (Farrar, Straus, Girous). Reviewed by Richard Bernstein.
</P>
