<P>
   CALIFORNIA -- CAET. U.S. Rep. Ellen Tauscher, D-Tassajara
Valley, generally declined Tuesday to say how women benefit from
her past two years in office, stating instead that men and women
benefit equally from policies she favors, such as a balanced
budget, child care and improved transportation. The comments were
delivered at a forum on women and the upcoming '98 election.
Stricherz
