go-ahead for Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to negotiate a deal
with the Palestinians in Washington later this week. By DEBORAH
HORAN.
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-BLAST (Mexico City) _ An explosion at an illegal
fireworks factory north of Mexico City flattens two city blocks and
kills at least 10 people. By ANDREW DOWNIE.
