<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 UPDATE &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Wednesday, October 14,
1998.
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Eds; Adds: BARR-WILLIAMS, LINDER-LITTMAN, TAINTED-MEAT
</P>
<P>
   This is the Cox News Service spot news budget for Wednesday,
October 14, 1998.
</P>
<P>
