<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-13 17:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4958 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRIBERY-CORRUPT-GLOBA     10-13 1802
