<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    TECH INDUSTRY PUSHES TO SAVE INTERNET TAX BAN
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARY BETH REGAN
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ E-commerce advocates are pressing Congress to save
a bill banning new Internet taxes, amid a flurry of last-minute
