 &HT;    SOUTHERN HAPPENINGS
 &HT;    By Paula Crouch Trasher
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   -- Chattanooga, Tenn. _ The Fall Color Cruise and Folk Festival
