opening Thursday at Rockingham Theatre at Market Place on Court
Square. Through Oct. 24. 540-564-1988.
</P>
<P>
   -- Charleston, S.C. _ The Preservation Society of Charleston
hosts the 22nd Annual Fall Candlelight Tours of Homes and Gardens
through Oct. 24. Candlelight tours of various historic districts
are 7-10 p.m. Thursday-Saturdays and Afternoon Garden Tours and Tea
is 2-5 p.m. Sunday. $30. Tickets: 1-800-968-8175.
</P>
<P>
   -- Asheville , N.C._ Biltmore Estate presents the second annual
Michaelmas: An English Harvest Fair through Oct. 25 (weekends
only). Arts and crafts, musical and theatrical entertainment,
children's activities, archery demonstrations, a grape stomp and
food and wine seminars. 1-800-323-6822.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
