<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-13 20:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5223 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LANDLORD-JAILED-AZR &LR;      10-13 0902
