<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED except: CANADA-BANKS,
HONDA-AD-COLUMN, CHIP-EARNINGS, EUROPE-BANKS, BUSINESS-TRAVEL,
FORD-FRIEDRICH, CULTURE-NOTES, BBA-VECSEY-COLUMN, BBA-YANKS-INDIANS
and BBN-BRAVES-PADRES.
